      "title": "Update in fuel for factories",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Sri Lanka Petroleum Private Tankers' Association says that fuel distribution for factories has commenced.",
        "The Chairman of the Lanka filling Station Owners Association Kumara Rajapaksa said that fuel will be released with restrictions.",
        "China says it will support consultations for SL debt solution"
